Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game
class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns a random value X where 0 \<= X \< range.

Usage
-----

float random( float range )

Parameters
----------

-   [range] - a number value that represents the largest possble value
    to be returned.

Examples
--------

This example generates a random number between `     min    ` and
`     max    `

     
    float min = 10;
    float max = 20;
     
    float rand = min + sys.random(max - min);

Notes
-----

Returns the same set of random numbers every time the game is run. Just
change the seed for a different set of numbers.

